{
  "texts": [
    "Future improvements in the PolyNetDWTCADx framework may be envisioned by the inclusion of advanced augmentation techniques, such as StyleGAN, in generating synthetic samples to handle class imbalance problems and further increase dataset diversity.",
    "Besides, the incorporation of either unsupervised or semisupervised learning methods might reduce the need for expensive labeled data and help in learning more robust feature representations from unlabeled samples.",
    "These would enhance the generalizability and scalability of the framework, enhancing performance, especially underrepresented classes and challenging segmentation tasks.",
    "RV-22 + DWT DEV-22 + DWT",
    "RV-22 + DWT + SVM DEV-22 + DWT + SVM"
  ]
}